
<div class="help">
  <h2>Controls:</h2>

  <p>Zoom: Mouse wheel, or drag context handles</p>
  <p>Pan: Drag graph or context area</p>
  <p>Draw Transits: Click to mark the center; click again to mark the boundary</p>
  <p>Focus: Click any marked transit, or a number on the right</p>
  <p>Delete Transit: Focus on transit, then click the X at right</p>
  <p>Continue to next light curve: Click FINISH button</p>
  <p>Finish and submit HIT</p>
  <a class="big-button">Return to Task</a>
</div>

